{"tid":1740752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解咁多人想區選如常進行","createTime":"2019-11-20T05:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T08:59:06.000Z","uid":38075,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"660ff1433a71c27900bcc8681b55197420c17042","tid":1740752,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"根本未光復前嘅選舉只係一個笑話<br />\n<br />\n種票，神奇票箱，一家人百家姓，污糟野層出不窮，港豬仲繼續打飛機安慰自己，繼續有險可守，血債票償，根本就係戇鳩又天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府其實唔會主動取消區選，因為佢根本可以靠唔同賤招食硬你，泛民建制一家親，香港人繼續含撚投票啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17a2fb96aa932cff27d127ebe7663106b24c4ef","tid":1740752,"uid":261082,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:06:01.000Z","msg":"咁你想點？全部唔好投最後保皇贏晒，跟住同全世界講香港人支持中共黑警？"},{"pid":"e9b3c5927dbedbd75fae2cf1e2560bafb227b4c1","tid":1740752,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:06:37.000Z","msg":"聽日出黎阿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PHmBHV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PHmBHV.png&h=52b0d6ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5499eb0795aba0ac5160b4f5e9262df9309322d","tid":1740752,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c17a2fb96aa932cff27d127ebe7663106b24c4ef","tid":1740752,"uid":261082,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:06:01.000Z","msg":"咁你想點？全部唔好投最後保皇贏晒，跟住同全世界講香港人支持中共黑警？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"開到花難道唔可以阻止投票？"},{"pid":"118fabb0cfee7567cd5d7bd035eb86ca37a82be7","tid":1740752,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"18-11-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9fee04d4d9d7368b595f78ee3fb583561f37d6bb","tid":1740752,"uid":28437,"like":0,"dislik